4819.text: [4819] link 'Current Darlington Lions President Pat de Martino presenting Tom Peacock with a medal at his home. Tom is sat in a grey armchair with a turquoise cushion behind him. He has a bald head with grey hair at the sides. He is wearing rectangular glasses, a blue zip up ribbed top over a lighter, greyish button up top and a white t-shirt. Pat has grey bobbed hair. She is wearing a ceremonial chain and a necklace made of large, multi-coloured beads. She has a blue V-necked jumper. Behind her is a light coloured sideboard on top of which sits lots of framed family photos.
